{"tid":665676,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"認真,價值投資,SASA必死","createTime":"2018-05-15T07:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T23:32:19.000Z","uid":109386,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad7d42d293d7c93d2554d6526781060d76daf10","tid":665676,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"我用178 SASA黎做例子,左邊係回報率,右邊係每股盈利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/143535_0481527be3816c05ddae106123e101fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F143535_0481527be3816c05ddae106123e101fd.png&h=3210c706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當預設投資回報率=美國10年息率 x 2.5 先值得去冒險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑線與橙線未來必定會相交</span>(蝕錢另計)<br />\n當黑線係橙線下面時<br />\n黑色線同橙色線相交原因有2個<br />\n1. 盈利上升\t\t\t<br />\n2. 股價下跌<br />\n藍線黑線同時下跌時為賣出訊號<br />\n而SASA會係第2個原因\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t<br />\n睇返張圖藍線,SASA由2014年開始,盈利一直倒退<br />\n但2016-2017年,盈利已經低過預設投資回報率<br />\n<br />\n藍黑線一齊向下,代表盈利倒退但股價上升<br />\n我認為呢個係<span style=\"color: red;\">市場不理性</span>投機行為<br />\n<br />\n最新數據,五一黃金周零售增長34.4%<br />\n我當SASA都一樣增長34.4%,同2015年相比都仲係差一倍<br />\n根據佢盈利走勢,現價買入SASA,未來回報率仲低過美國10年債"},{"pid":"9b8f9dc35b93540684e1f2dac408f095e4d1fc11","tid":665676,"uid":117947,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"咁多燈神入面，都係打哥最pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748fde7a23679be9aad7631d2c6d5c6acbea4c94","tid":665676,"uid":129507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"Pro"},{"pid":"cf17b4319c795ae8124c520200624cd790fa5bdf","tid":665676,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"唔知你想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273be4548d0c4485959e212e893efeaca78e171c","tid":665676,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9